<DIV1 TYPE="sermon">
<PB N="1" REF="002256_0035_0FDADD7C00F42400">
<HEAD>The Nature of Early Piety as it re&s;pects <HI>Men.</HI></HEAD>
<BYLINE>By Mr. <HI>Colman.</HI> Bo&s;ton-Lecture, April 6. 1721.</BYLINE>
<EPIGRAPH>
<Q><BIBL><HI>EPHESIANS VI. 2.</HI></BIBL>
<P>Honour thy Father and Mother, which is the Fir&s;t Commandment with Promi&s;e.</P></Q>
