<P>_ON the la&s;t Lecture the <HI>Na|ture of Early Piety</HI> was &s;tated and explained <HI>as it re&s;pects the Glorious GOD;</HI> that is to &s;ay, the Duty of Young People toward Him their <HI>Creator</HI> and <HI>Redeemer</HI> was laid before them; that which follows next in Order, and which <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">herefore falls to me (in the Cour&s;e and Me|thod
