<P>BUT by <HI>Father</HI> and <HI>Mother</HI> as you are to <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">nder&s;tand fir&s;tly and chiefly your proper <HI>Parents,</HI> your Natural Father who begat thee, <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">nd thy Mother who bare thee, &s;o al&s;o tho&s;e <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">hat may &s;tand in the <HI>Place</HI> of Parents to thee, <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">o who&s;e Care and Government you may be <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ommitted if you are <HI>Orphans,</HI> or by whom <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ou may be <HI>Adopted,</HI> or being de&s;titute and <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">elple&s;s may be <HI>ca&s;t upon</HI> by the Providence <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">f GOD.</P>
