<P>WHEREFORE <HI>(Children)</HI> mind it, both <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">he <HI>Precept</HI> and the <HI>Promi&s;e</HI> mean that <HI>from a <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ous heart and mind,</HI> from a principle of Grace <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ithin you, in a religious manner and for <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">ly Ends; for the honour of God and for <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">our own Eternal Salvation, you ob&s;erve <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">e&s;e Duties which are <HI>this Day</HI> Preach'd to <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">u from <HI>the&s;e Words.</HI></P>
