<PB N="7" REF="002256_0038_0FDADD80B9C7EE60"><HI>that it may be well with thee, and thou maye&s;t live long upon the Earth;</HI> as are the Words after my <HI>Text.</HI> "You mu&s;t eye the <HI>Command|ment</HI> of God in the <HI>fir&s;t</HI> place, (obey your Parents <HI>in the Lord,</HI> becau&s;e He commands it, and in all things that are agreeable to His Will; becau&s;e <HI>this is right</HI> and ju&s;t, by the Law of <HI>Nature</HI> and <HI>Nations</HI> as well as by the <HI>written Word</HI>) and <HI>then</HI> have re&s;pect unto the <HI>Recom|pence of Reward.</HI></P>
